Global Gluten-free Digestive Cookies Market Insights
Gluten-free Digestive Cookies Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Gluten-free Digestive Cookies Market Overview
The global gluten-free digestive cookies market is projected to reach a value of USD 1.7 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.2% from 2025 to 2030. This growth can be attributed to the rising demand for gluten-free products, particularly among individuals with celiac disease or gluten sensitivities. Consumers are increasingly prioritizing healthier snack options, and gluten-free cookies fit into these preferences. Furthermore, the increasing adoption of plant-based and natural ingredients in food products has also contributed to the market's expansion. Additionally, the rise in disposable income and changing dietary habits have also influenced the demand for gluten-free digestive cookies globally.

